wvw.mlod.repo.drug

Class DrugRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • wvw.mlod.repo.Repository
      • wvw.mlod.repo.drug.DrugRepository
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregatedDrugRepository, Drugbank, Drugcentral

    public abstract class DrugRepository
extends Repository
    A drug repository in the "MLOD cloud". It has methods for finding and loading drugs, drug categories and health conditions, as well as finding DDI and DCI. It is centered on a drug-ontology that can be found in src/main/resources/schema/drug.owl. A subclass only needs to implement the execute(String) method.
